snippet.title: Hillary Clinton And Bernie Sanders' Campaigns Diverge | MSNBC

localized.description:
Hillary Clinton has now set her sights on the general election and Donald Trump, while Bernie Sanders has vowed to take the fight all the way to the convention. NBC’s Chris Jansing reports from Fort Wayne, Indiana on the upcoming agendas and strategies of both campaigns.
